body:
This PR integrates accumulated LST algorithm developments held back during the review of the LST integration (cms-sw/cmssw#45117). The full list of PRs that are included here can be found in https://github.com/SegmentLinking/cmssw/issues/117. This is our first step in our list of follow-up tasks (https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/issues/46746).

The changes include bug fixes and algorithmic improvements, but they also start to address follow-up comments from the integration PR. In particular, the LST README was updated (addressing https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45117#discussion_r1681737544 and https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45117#discussion_r1681741075), the pT threshold is now configurable (addressing https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45117#discussion_r1749245650), and the first bullet point of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45117#issuecomment-2479912047 was fixed.

@slava77 @VourMa
